DarkMouse::
"Eh, OK. So he's a little more motivated than most of us. I'll stay 
out os his way, he'll stay out of mine. And we all watch out for 
Chamaleon's well being. Anything else to worry about?"  She was in in 
a strange mood. She knew she could take the beating of a lifetime and 
still survive it when a lot of bots wouldn't.  But lately, she really 
didn't care if she lived or not.  She was a mouse. What good could 
small rodent do?
